default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultHow have other countries incentivised CCS development? How successful have they been? How do they compare to the UK’s efforts? default8.1.default&#xa0;&#xa0; 
default 
defaultAs outlined earlier the Norwegian Government has part funded a cement pilot plant in Brevik, Norway. The UK Government has been slow to develop industrial CCS in the UK and appears to have a preference for carrying out studies and holding workshops instead
default of formulating 
defaulta funding programme to 
defaultfacilitate
default the development 
defaultof industrial CCS in the UK.
